  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the Russian and German war started, because we had one war in '39, and the second war just started between Russia and Germany, which started in [NON-ENGLISH], 1941.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, uh, since, uh, things got hard in [NON-ENGLISH], which was, uh, getting practically impossible to obtain food and obtain food that you could eat because the food got so horrible that even you were hungry, you know, you couldn't swallow it.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my brother and I decided to leave that place because, as far we could hear the news, that the Germans are getting closer and that was not where we wanted to be-- closer to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] In the meantime, uh, the-- what do you call it in English?-- the commissioner, from, the military commissioner in that little town, he met my brother and I and he said, why don't you induct, he said, to the Polish Army?",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a Polish army already created in Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, uh, so we were thinking maybe it's a good idea.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in the meantime, we got to-- some word that Russia is having an amnesty for Polish people that were in-- in camps, in labor camps, in Russia.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're releasing them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is the element they're going to induct in that Polish army that's being created in Russia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they should go to the Middle East, fight the Germans over Afghanistan, and through Iran.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, uh, but we had to go to-- to Central Asia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is where the-- the headquarters was for-- to induct Polish citizens, you know, to gather them and-- and send them overseas.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my brother and I decided we're going to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
